title: Episode 93: The Secrets of Interviews (w/ Allen Huffcutt)
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In our amazing third episode of the season, we had the pleasure of speaking to Dr. Allen Huffcutt. He sheds light on the psychology of interviews and how psychology has a part to play in business and the world at large. You do not want to miss this episode!
